title: Jose Mourinho wants Kyle Walker at Fenerbahce
description: Fenerbahce manager Jose Mourinho wants to sign Kyle Walker from Manchester City in the summer transfer window, according to The Times. Walker spent the second half of last season on loan at AC Milan, who have decided not to make the deal permanent. title: Atletico Madrid target Liverpool left-back Andy Robertson
description: Atletico Madrid are interested in signing Andy Robertson from Liverpool in the summer transfer window, according to The Guardian. With Milos Kerkez edging closer to a £45million move to the Premier League champions from Bournemouth, La Liga club Atletico believe that the door has opened for them to bring Scotland international left-back Robertson.
